quran[71]{c,v,t}:
  80,1,Jwautile sinya (Muhammadi ﷺ) ni kulola kumbali
  80,2,Ligongo lyakum’bichiilila jwangalola
  80,3,Ana chichi chachimmanyisye kuti mwine jwalakwejo kuŵa nkuliswejesya (ku ilemwa)
  80,4,"Mwine chakumbuchile, basi nikunkamuchisya kumbuchilako"
  80,5,Nambo mundu jwaliweni kusichila
  80,6,Basi jwalakwejo mmwe ni nkunkosoŵalila
  80,7,Pangalitu ulemwa kukwenu naga ngaakuliswejesya (ku ukafili)
  80,8,Nambo mundu jwam’bichilile aku juchikangamalaga
  80,9,Soni jwalakwejo ali nkun'jogopa (Allah)
  80,10,Basi ya jwalakwejo mmwe ni nkuikwanjila
  80,11,Ngwamba (ngasintenda iyyo)! Chisimu galakwe (ma Ȃyaga) gaŵele chikumbusyo
  80,12,Basi jwaakusaka talikumbusye najo (Qur’anijo)
  80,13,(Jili) mu ikalakala yakuchimbichikwa
  80,14,"Yapenani, yakuswejesyedwa"
  80,15,Ili m’makono mwa akulemba (Achimalaika)
  80,16,"Ŵakuchimbichika, ŵaakunda (malamusi)"
  80,17,"Pamasile palaniwe mundu (kafili), kanila kwakwe kwalakweku ni kwantiuli"
  80,18,Ana an'gumbile kuumila mu chinduchi
  80,19,"Kuumila m’mesi (gaŵalume ni ŵakongwe) an'gumbile, ni kumpanjila mpango (wakagumbidwe kakwe)"
  80,20,Kaneka naakun'jepepachisyaga litala (lyakopochela ku duniya)
  80,21,Kaneko nakasampaga chiwa ni kunsiika m’malembe
  80,22,Soni patachisakapo tachinsyusya
  80,23,Ngwamba! Chisimu (kafili) nganakwanilisyepe yannamwile (Allah)
  80,24,Basi achetelele mundu ya yakulya yakwe
  80,25,Chisimu Uwwe tukasakusula mesi (gawula) mwamachili
  80,26,Kaneka ni tukasaligangaga litaka kuliganga kusyene
  80,27,Ni tukasakoposya mwalakwemo songolo
  80,28,Kwisa soni isogosi ya zabibu ni maupulu (gakulya ilango)
  80,29,Ni kwisa soni isogosi ya zaituni (yakwenga mauta) ni itela yatende
  80,30,Ni migunda jaitela yejinji
  80,31,Kwisa soni isogosi (yamitundu mitundu) ni mopo
  80,32,(Kuŵa) yakunsengwasya ŵanganyammwe ni ilango yenu
  80,33,Basi ndema jaliichiika lipenga lyakusiŵa m’mawiwi (ligongo lya machili gakwe)
  80,34,Lyele lisikulyo mundu tachatila achimwenegwe
  80,35,Kwisa soni mamagwe ni babagwe
  80,36,Ni kwisa soni ŵankwakwe ni ŵanache ŵakwe
  80,37,Mundu jwalijose mwa ŵanganyao lyele lisikulyo tachikola yakunkwanila (kuntendekasya kuti akakosoŵalila ya jwine)
  80,38,Ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiŵa syakumelemenda
  80,39,Syakusechelela ni kusengwa (pakupikana yakuja ku Mbepo)
  80,40,Sano ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichipakala luwundu
  80,41,Sichiŵa siunichilidwe ni chipi
  80,42,Ŵanganyao ni ŵali achimakafili ŵakusakasya nnope
  81,1,Pandema jalichikulunjidwa lyuŵa (nikutyoka lilanguka lyakwe)
  81,2,Ni ndema jasichipatuka ndondwa
  81,3,Ni ndema jagachijendesyedwa matumbi (paagachuŵa m’mangwakwe)
  81,4,Ni ndema jasichilechedwa ngamiya syana maŵele gepele
  81,5,Ni ndema jaichisonganganyisyidwa inyama yamwitinji
  81,6,Ni ndema jasichikolesyedwa mbwani moto
  81,7,Ni ndema jajichilumbikanyisyidwa mitima (ku ilu yakwe)
  81,8,Ni ndema jachachiwusyidwa mwanache jwankwongwe jwaŵasichidwe ali jwaumi
  81,9,Kuti ŵawulajidwe ni ulemwachi
  81,10,Ni ndema jaichipindikulidwa ikalakala (mugalembedwe masengo gamundu)
  81,11,Ni ndema jalichitandukulidwa liwunde
  81,12,Ni ndema jauchikwisilidwa Moto Waukali
  81,13,Ni ndema jajichiŵandichisyidwa Mbepo
  81,14,Mundu jwalijose tachimanyilila yayiche nayo
  81,15,Basi ngusilumbila ndondwa syasikusisika muusi
  81,16,(Ni) syasikwendaga (chilo kaneka) ni kusisika pakutiŵila
  81,17,Ni nguchilumbila soni chilo ndema jachikwika ni kutyoka
  81,18,Ni ngukulumbila soni kumasikusiku ndema jakukulanguka
  81,19,Chisimu aji (Qur’aniji) gaŵele maloŵe ga (kulungusyidwa ni) Ntenga Jwakuchimbichika (Jibulilu)
  81,20,"Nsyene machili, soni jwana uchimbichimbi wapenani kwa (Allah) Nsyene Arishi (Chindanda Chaulungu)"
  81,21,Jwakundidwa malamusi kwinaniko (ni Achimalaika) soni jwakulupichika
  81,22,Soni Nnongo n'jenuju (Muhammadi ﷺ) nganaŵa jwamasoka
  81,23,Soni chisimu chene (Muhammadi ﷺ) ŵam'bweni jwalakwe (Jibulilu mu kagumbidwe kakwe kasyesyene) kuchipelela chameso chakuonechela (cha ku ngopoko lyuŵa)
  81,24,Soni jwalakwe nganijuŵa jwausuchi pa (umanyilisi wa) yakusisika
  81,25,Soni aji (Qur’an) nganigaŵa maloŵe ga shetani jwakuŵinjidwa
  81,26,Nambi kwapi nkuja
  81,27,Nganijiŵa aji (Qur’an) ikaŵeje chikumbusyo cha iwumbe yosope
  81,28,Kwa mundu jwaakusaka mwa jenumanja kuti ajongoche
  81,29,"Ni nganim'ba nsachile, ikaŵeje akasache kaje Allah M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope"